INSERT INTO exchange_feature_support (exchangeSlug, featureSlug, supported, levelZh, levelEn, detailZh, detailEn, maxLeverage, feeInfo, highlight) VALUES
('binance','spot',1,'旗舰级','Flagship','全球最大现货市场，支持1400+交易对，订单簿深度全球第一。支持限价单、市价单、止盈止损单、OCO订单等多种订单类型。BNB持有者享受25%手续费折扣。','World largest spot market with 1400+ pairs and deepest order book globally. Supports limit, market, stop-limit, OCO orders. BNB holders get 25% fee discount.','10x','Maker 0.1% / Taker 0.1%（BNB折扣后0.075%）',1),
('binance','futures',1,'旗舰级','Flagship','全球最大合约交易所，USDT本位和币本位永续合约，支持125倍杠杆。提供交割合约（季度/双季度），24小时交易量超200亿美元。','Worlds largest futures exchange. USDT-margined and coin-margined perpetuals with up to 125x leverage. Quarterly delivery contracts available. $20B+ daily volume.','125x','Maker 0.02% / Taker 0.04%',1),
('binance','margin',1,'完善','Complete','支持全仓和逐仓杠杆，最高10倍杠杆，支持600+杠杆交易对。提供自动借贷还款功能，利率根据市场供需动态调整。','Full cross and isolated margin with up to 10x leverage, 600+ margin pairs. Auto-borrow and auto-repay. Interest rates adjust dynamically.','10x','同现货费率',0),
('binance','tradfi',1,'领先','Leading','Binance Stock Tokens：提供特斯拉、苹果、谷歌等美股代币化产品（部分地区可用）。支持黄金、白银等大宗商品代币。','Binance Stock Tokens: tokenized US stocks like Tesla, Apple, Google (region-dependent). Supports gold and silver commodity tokens.','N/A','同现货费率',0),
('binance','earn',1,'旗舰级','Flagship','活期理财（Flexible Savings）、定期理财、BNB Vault、流动性挖矿、ETH/BNB质押、双币投资（Dual Investment）。年化收益最高可达20%+（高风险产品）。','Flexible Savings, Fixed Deposits, BNB Vault, Liquidity Mining, ETH/BNB staking, Dual Investment. APY up to 20%+ for high-risk products.','N/A','无额外费用',1),
('binance','web3',1,'旗舰级','Flagship','Binance Web3 Wallet内置于App，支持ETH/BNB Chain/Arbitrum/Polygon等50+链。可直接访问DeFi协议、NFT市场、跨链桥。MPC技术无需助记词。','Built-in Binance Web3 Wallet supports 50+ chains. Direct DeFi, NFT, and cross-chain access. MPC technology - no seed phrase needed.','N/A','Gas费由用户承担',1),
('binance','options',1,'完善','Complete','欧式期权（European Options），支持BTC和ETH。提供每日、每周、每月到期合约，可使用USDT作为保证金。','European-style options for BTC and ETH. Daily, weekly, monthly expiry. USDT as collateral.','N/A','Maker 0.02% / Taker 0.03%',0),
('binance','copy',1,'完善','Complete','跟单交易功能，可复制精英交易员的合约策略。交易员需通过审核，显示历史收益率、最大回撤等数据。','Copy trading for futures strategies. Traders must pass review. Shows historical ROI, max drawdown, and other metrics.','N/A','跟单利润分成10-20%',0),
('binance','community',1,'旗舰级','Flagship','币安广场（Binance Square）：全球最大加密社交平台，数百万用户发布内容，支持关注KOL、话题讨论、实时行情评论。','Binance Square: worlds largest crypto social platform with millions of users. Follow KOLs, join topic discussions, real-time market commentary.','N/A','免费',1),
('binance','bot',1,'完善','Complete','网格交易机器人（现货/合约）、定投机器人（DCA）、套利机器人。支持自定义参数或使用AI推荐配置。','Grid trading bots (spot/futures), DCA bots, arbitrage bots. Custom parameters or AI-recommended configurations.','N/A','策略收益分成',0),
('binance','otc',1,'旗舰级','Flagship','币安OTC门户，支持大额法币和加密货币兑换，最低$10,000起，提供专属报价，不影响市场价格，支持100+法币。','Binance OTC Portal for large fiat/crypto conversions. Minimum $10,000, dedicated quotes, 100+ fiat currencies supported.','N/A','含在报价内',0),
('binance','launchpad',1,'旗舰级','Flagship','Binance Launchpad（代币销售）和Launchpool（质押挖矿）。历史项目包括Axie Infinity、Stepn等，平均首日涨幅超200%。需持有BNB参与。','Binance Launchpad (token sales) and Launchpool (staking mining). Historical projects include Axie Infinity, Stepn. Average first-day gain 200%+. Requires BNB.','N/A','免费参与',1),
('binance','ecosystem',1,'旗舰级','Flagship','BNB（平台币）：市值前5，用于手续费折扣、Launchpad参与、DeFi质押。BNB Chain（BSC）：全球最活跃公链之一，每日交易量数百万笔。Binance NFT市场。','BNB token: top-5 market cap, used for fee discounts, Launchpad, DeFi staking. BNB Chain: one of worlds most active chains. Binance NFT marketplace.','N/A','N/A',1)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE detailZh=VALUES(detailZh);
